                    <div class="h-0.5 w-10 bg-sunburst mb-4"></div>
                    <p class="text-charcoal-light text-body-sm leading-relaxed">By using this site, you represent that you are at least the age of majority in your state or province of residence, or that you are the age of majority in your state or province of residence and you have given us your consent to allow any of your minor dependents to use this site.</p>
                </li>

                <li>
                    <h2 class="text-charcoal font-bold text-h3 mb-1">Section 8 &mdash; Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <div class="h-0.5 w-10 bg-sunburst mb-4"></div>
